text: Josefin Taljegård (born 26 August 1995) is a Swedish figure skater. She is the 2019 Coupe du Printemps champion, the 2018 Nordics bronze medalist, and a two- time Swedish national bronze medalist. At the 2013 World Junior Championships, she qualified to the free skate and finished 24th overall. == Programs == {|class=wikitable style=text-align:center ! Season ! Short program !
